Bio Graphy

Meet the 6'3" model

Malaica Kokane is a 24 year old Indian model/Influencer living in the United Kingdom/India.
Standing tall at 190.5 cms, Malaica has been a part of reality shows including India's Next Top Model S4, The Antisocial Network and Pyaar Tune Kya Kiya.
She has walked the ramp for various designers and modelled for numerous brands including Bombay Times Fashion Week 2021 for designer Rohit Verma, INIFD Launchpad for Lakme Fashion Week, Zeiss, Schwarzkopf, Rohit Anand Salon, Livon Serum, The Arab Crab and Eye Candy.
Malaica has also dabbled in various physical pursuits as she is a national level Basketball player, Rhythmic Gymnast and an Athlete. Currently, she is working in London in the corporate sector.
